content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 316.6 - Products not to be removed from official establishments unless marked in accordance with the regulations

State Regulations

No person shall remove or cause to be removed from an
official establishment any products which the regulations in this Article
require to be marked in any way unless they are clearly and legibly marked in
compliance with such regulations. Notes
